sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant Init as argoexec (init)<br/>Artifact Download
    participant User as User Container<br/>Workflow Step
    participant Wait as argoexec (wait)<br/>Artifact Upload
    participant S3 as Artifact Repository<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant SQL as SQL Database<br/>5432/TCP (optional)

    Note over DSP,SQL: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: POST Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    activate K8s

    WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRDs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow Created Event
    deactivate K8s

    WFC->>K8s: Create Pod (with argoexec sidecar)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    activate K8s
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod Scheduled
    deactivate K8s

    activate Pod
    Init->>S3: Download Input Artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key / SA Key
    S3-->>Init: Artifact Data

    activate User
    Note over User: Execute workflow step<br/>(user container runs)
    User-->>Wait: Step completes (exit code)
    deactivate User

    Wait->>S3: Upload Output Artifacts<br/>(tar+gzip to shared volume)<br/>Auth: Access Key / SA Key
    S3-->>Wait: Upload Confirmed

    Wait->>K8s: Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    deactivate Pod

    WFC->>K8s: Watch WorkflowTaskResults<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: TaskResult Event

    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow Status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    opt Workflow Archiving Enabled
        WFC->>SQL: Archive Workflow<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    end

    Note over DSP,SQL: Flow 2: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    WFC->>K8s: Watch CronWorkflow CRDs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: CronWorkflow Event

    Note over WFC: Cron worker evaluates schedule

    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow from CronWorkflow<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over WFC: Triggers Flow 1 for created Workflow
